    <item>
      <title>莫里森寻求为 12 亿英镑杠杆贷款再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/morrisons-seeks-to-refinance-1-2-billion-in-leveraged-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国食品杂货商莫里森正在为 12 亿英镑（16 亿美元）的杠杆贷款进行再融资，希望利用投资者对高收益债务的强劲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/morrisons-seeks-to-refinance-1-2-billion-in-leveraged-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 10:02:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求疲软导致中国贷款表现令人失望，但债券提振信贷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管信贷增长超过预期（主要得益于国债销售激增），9月份中国贷款扩张表现令人失望，表明国内需求仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-s-credit-expansion-tops-forecasts-but-loans-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 09:17:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据媒体报道，印尼下任总统将召集部长候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indonesia-s-next-president-calls-up-possible-ministers-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚当选总统普拉博沃·苏比安托本周晚些时候就职之前将确定内阁名单，届时他可能会任命几位现任官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/indonesia-s-next-president-calls-up-possible-ministers-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 08:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
